data.description: Nestled peacefully on a serene street in Lake Los Angeles, this charming high desert gem boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a spacious 1,584 square feet of living space, all resting on an expansive 29,616 square foot lot. Adding to its allure, this home offers an attached 2-car garage for your convenience. Upon entering, you'll be welcomed into a generously sized living room featuring a vaulted ceiling, elegant wood floors, and a cozy fireplace – the perfect spot to unwind and create lasting memories with friends and family. Large windows and a sliding glass door bathe the room in natural light, creating a warm and inviting ambiance. Adjacent to the living room, you'll find a well-appointed kitchen and a dining area. The dining area provides ample counterspace and storage, making it an ideal space to bring your culinary aspirations to life. Three spacious bedrooms await, each offering comfort and tranquility. The primary suite boasts an attached bathroom for added privacy and convenience, while all bedrooms are bathed in natural light through their windows. Step outside to discover a vast backyard, complete with a pool and spa (currently empty), waiting for your creative touch. This outdoor space is a blank canvas, allowing you to bring your vision to life, whether that means lush landscaping, an outdoor oasis, or a play area for family and friends.
